room_title: Escape room "Tin Star Saloon" by Escape Room Marlton in Collingswood
room_description: The Tin Star Saloon served the best Sarsaparilla on this side of the Mississippi, but it has fallen on hard times. Most folks have cleared out, and you know this is your last chance to find the secret recipe before the bandits ride in. You're ready to head West, but make a quick stop in the saloon hoping you'll find one last batch and save the recipe. Low on ammunition, and ill-prepared for a gun fight, you must be out of here before the bandits arrive in an hour!
